wardenips (0.2.3-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of WardenIPS v0.2.3
  * Professional CLI wrapper with colorized output
  * ASN-based threat detection with Loyalsoldier/geoip integration
  * Autonomous weekly GeoLite2 database updates
  * Full source IP visibility in dashboard (no truncation)
  * Blocklist protection with AbuseIPDB curated data
  * Real-time intrusion prevention with ipset/iptables
  * Live operational dashboard with admin console
  * Plugin-based detection (SSH, Minecraft, Nginx)
  * Systemd service integration

